<template>
  <!-- 搜索区 -->
  <el-row align="middle">
    <el-col :span="4">
      <el-text tag="b" size="large"> Category </el-text>
    </el-col>

    <el-col :span="10">
      <el-space direction="vertical">
        <el-text tag="b" size="large"> Product1 </el-text>
        <el-select
          v-model="product1"
          clearable
          filterable
          placeholder="Select"
          @change="searchProduct1Pictures"

            :key="index"
            :label="item"
            :value="item"
          />

      </el-space>
    </el-col>

    <el-col :span="10">

        <el-select
          v-model="product2"
          clearable
          filterable
          placeholder="Select"
          @change="searchProduct2Pictures"
        >

            v-for="(item, index) in productList"
            :key="index"
            :label="item"
            :value="item"
          />
        </el-select>
      </el-space>
    </el-col>
  </el-row>

  <el-divider />


</template>
